snippet: Now in its third year of existence, the Florida women’s lacrosse program has blazed its way to the top of the sport, earning a No. 1 national ranking and the top overall seed in the N.C.A.A. tournament.
abstract: University of Florida's women's lacrosse program has blazed its way to the top of the sport, earning a No. 1 national ranking and the top overall seed in the NCAA tournament.
lead_paragraph: Now in its third year of existence, the Florida women’s lacrosse program has blazed its way to the top of the sport, earning a No. 1 national ranking and the top overall seed in the N.C.A.A. tournament.

headline.seo: Florida Wastes No Time in Becoming a Force in Women’s Lacrosse
